Description_lang: $?a137005[Death's Due]?a212611[The Hunt]?a137009[Convoke the Spirits]?a137014[Wild Spirits]?a137018[Shifting Power]?a137022[Faeline Stomp]?a137026[Blessing of Seasons]?a137030[Fae Guardians]?a137034[Sepsis]?a137038[Fae Transfusion]?a137042[Soul Rot]?a137047[Ancient Aftershock]?a353167[Boon of the Covenants][Activating your Night Fae class ability] puts flowers at your feet for ${$342761d*$<mod>}.1 sec that increase your Haste by $342774s1% while you stand with them.

description_blz.en_US: Shifting Power puts flowers at your feet for 12.0 sec that increase your Haste by 15% while you stand with them.
description_blz.es_MX: Poder cambiante coloca flores a tus pies durante 12.0 s, que aumentan tu celeridad un 15% mientras permaneces en ese lugar.
description_blz.pt_BR: Poder Cambiante cria flores aos seus pés por 12,0 s, que aumentam em 15% a Aceleração enquanto ficar em cima delas.
description_blz.de_DE: Wenn Ihr 'Machtverschiebung' aktiviert, sprießen Blumen zu Euren Füßen, die 12,0 Sek. lang bestehen bleiben und Euer Tempo um 15% erhöhen, solange Ihr Euch im Effektbereich aufhaltet.
description_blz.en_GB: Shifting Power puts flowers at your feet for 12.0 sec that increase your Haste by 15% while you stand with them.
description_blz.es_ES: Poder cambiante pone a tus pies durante 12,0 s unas flores que aumentan un 15% tu celeridad mientras permaneces junto a ellas.
description_blz.fr_FR: Puissance fluctuante dépose des fleurs à vos pieds pendant 12,0 s. Celles-ci vous confèrent un bonus de 15% à la Hâte tant que vous restez à proximité.
description_blz.it_IT: Potere Mutevole fa crescere ai tuoi piedi dei fiori, che aumentano la celerità del 15% per 12,0 s quando si sta nell'area d'effetto.
description_blz.ru_RU: При использовании "Переходящей силы" на 12,0 сек. создает у ваших ног цветы, повышающие скорость на 15%, пока вы в них стоите.
description_blz.ko_KR: 힘의 전환 사용 시 12.0초 동안 발밑에 꽃밭을 피워나게 합니다. 꽃밭 안에 서 있는 동안 가속이 15%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 法能移轉可使你腳下綻放鮮花，持續12.0秒，只要站在效果範圍內，你的加速提高15%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 变易幻能[激活你的法夜职业技能]会在你的脚边放置鲜花，持续12.0秒。在此期间当你站在鲜花旁时，会使你的急速提高15%。
